Package: Firehose
Title: An R Markdown-based report building tool for analysts and SPC users in the NHS #plotthedots style
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Tom", "Smith", , "tomsmith_uk@hotmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Pass data and some configuration in, and this package will use RMarkdown to 
    render report outputs using SPC XmR charts, and run charts, allowing 
    analysts to reduce time spent writing reports, and increase time spent 
    doing analysis.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
Imports: 
    beepr,
    rmarkdown
